---
description: Portfolio project rules
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

- Keep code beginner-friendly and readable
- Prefer modular functions over large scripts
- Explain what files were added or changed
- Do not generate the whole project at once
- Implement one milestone at a time
- Suggest tests for important logic
- Keep the project GitHub-ready
- Update README after major features
- Suggest a clean Git commit message after each milestone